 →GoToTidyUp 2≠#._Fire.Fire.Replace.NoOfReplacements
 →GoToTidyUp 1≠+/'whole Universe'⍷∊⎕SRC #.TestData.ScriptedNamespaces.ToBeChanged_1
 →GoToTidyUp 1≠+/'whole Universe'⍷∊⎕SRC #.TestData.ScriptedNamespaces.ToBeChanged_2
